name: Midtown East
description: Now you are in Midtown East. Midtown East is a huge tourist, commercial and residential area. Around 5th Ave, the neighborhood is home to many tourist attractions, such as St. Patrick's Cathedral and Rockefeller Center. Moving towards 3rd Ave and further east, the area is more residential, and generally, the restaurants are better and more affordable. There are tons of famous attractions for both adults and children in Midtown.
